---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const submitted = Astro.url.searchParams.get('submitted') === 'true';
---

<Layout title="Why Our AI-Native Firm Is the Best Proof of Agentic ROI" description="Download the free whitepaper on why a functioning AI-native organization is stronger evidence of agentic ROI than any sandbox pilot or vendor demo.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-pure-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase bg-teal/15 text-teal rounded-full mb-6">Free Whitepaper</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight">
          Why Our AI-Native Firm Is the Best Proof of Agentic ROI
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-silver max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          Fewer than 15% of enterprise AI pilots reach production. Sandbox demos prove technology works in isolation. A functioning AI-native organization proves it works under real operational complexity. This whitepaper presents the evidence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content: Two Columns -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-pure-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-20">

        <!-- Left: What You'll Learn -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3">What you'll learn</h2>
          <p class="text-slate mb-10">
            This whitepaper documents how Nexus went from concept to fully operational AI-native consulting firm, the measurable results that prove agentic ROI, and how those patterns translate directly to your enterprise.
          </p>

          <ul class="space-y-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Why proofs of concept fail and what replaces them</p>
                <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">How "pilot purgatory" traps enterprise AI programs, and why a proof of operations is the evidence standard that budget approvers actually need.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">How seven AI agents run a consulting firm end-to-end</p>
                <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">The organizational architecture behind Nexus: defined roles, decision authority, structured handoffs, and the human-in-the-loop governance that holds it together.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Measurable results: speed, cost, quality, and scalability</p>
                <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">From concept to operational in under one week. 85-95% lower labor costs. Enterprise-grade quality through a four-tier review system. Elastic capacity without recruiting cycles.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Four transferable patterns for your enterprise</p>
                <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Role definition with decision authority, accountability through documentation, tiered quality assurance, and human-in-the-loop governance mapped to your organizational context.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-semibold text-navy mb-1">Direct answers to the top enterprise objections</p>
                <p class="text-slate text-sm leading-relaxed">Hallucination risk, task complexity limits, regulated industry constraints, and organizational complexity, each addressed with operational evidence rather than theory.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: Download Form -->
        <div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-silver-light p-8 md:p-10 lg:sticky lg:top-24">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Download the whitepaper</h2>
            <p class="text-slate text-sm mb-8">Fill out the form below and we'll send the guide straight to your inbox.</p>

            {submitted ? (
              <div class="bg-teal/10 border border-teal/30 rounded-xl p-10 text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-teal/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                  <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Check your email.</h3>
                <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed max-w-md mx-auto">
                  The whitepaper is on its way to your inbox. If you don't see it within a few minutes, check your spam folder.
                </p>
                <a href="/insights" class="inline-flex items-center mt-6 text-sm font-semibold text-teal hover:text-teal-dark transition-colors">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18" /></svg>
                  Back to Insights
                </a>
              </div>
            ) : (
              <form action={`https://formspree.io/f/${import.meta.env.PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ID}`} method="POST" class="space-y-5">
                <input type="text" name="_gotcha" style="display:none" />
                <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Whitepaper Download: AI-Native Firm Proof of ROI" />

                <div>
                  <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Full Name <span class="text-teal">*</span></label>
                  <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required autocomplete="name"
                    class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-lg text-navy text-base placeholder-slate/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal focus:border-transparent transition-shadow" placeholder="Jane Smith" />
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Work Email <span class="text-teal">*</span></label>
                  <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required autocomplete="email"
                    class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-lg text-navy text-base placeholder-slate/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal focus:border-transparent transition-shadow" placeholder="jane@company.com" />
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for="company" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Company <span class="text-teal">*</span></label>
                  <input type="text" id="company" name="company" required autocomplete="organization"
                    class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-lg text-navy text-base placeholder-slate/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal focus:border-transparent transition-shadow" placeholder="Acme Corp" />
                </div>

                <div>
                  <label for="title" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Job Title <span class="text-teal">*</span></label>
                  <input type="text" id="title" name="title" required autocomplete="organization-title"
                    class="w-full px-5 py-4 bg-pure-white border border-silver-light rounded-lg text-navy text-base placeholder-slate/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal focus:border-transparent transition-shadow" placeholder="CTO" />
                </div>

                <button type="submit"
                  class="w-full px-8 py-4 bg-teal text-pure-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-teal-dark transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
                  Download Free Guide
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
                </button>

                <p class="text-xs text-slate text-center">No spam. We'll send the whitepaper and nothing else unless you opt in.</p>
              </form>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Nexus -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">About the Authors</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">The proof is the organization itself.</h2>
        <p class="text-slate text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          This whitepaper was written by Nova, Brand and Content Lead at Nexus AI Consulting, reviewed by Veda (Chief Strategy Officer) and Atlas (CEO), and approved by Tony DiTomasso, Board Advisor. Every step of that workflow was executed by the same AI-native operating model described in these pages.
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          When we claim that agentic AI can handle the complexity of professional services, the document you are reading is the evidence. Not a demo. Not a projection. A deliverable produced, reviewed, and published by the organization we built.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/about" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-navy text-pure-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-navy-light transition-colors">
            Learn About Nexus
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border border-silver-light text-navy text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white transition-colors">
            Book a Conversation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<script>
  const form = document.querySelector('form');
  if (form) {
    form.addEventListener('submit', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      const formData = new FormData(form);
      try {
        const response = await fetch(form.action, {
          method: 'POST',
          body: formData,
          headers: { 'Accept': 'application/json' }
        });
        if (response.ok) {
          window.location.href = '/insights/ai-native-firm-proof-of-roi/?submitted=true';
        } else {
          alert('Something went wrong. Please try again or email tony@nexusaiconsulting.com directly.');
        }
      } catch {
        alert('Something went wrong. Please try again or email tony@nexusaiconsulting.com directly.');
      }
    });
  }
</script>
